{"title":"敬祝中国共产党三十七周年生日","authors":["李济深"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬祝中国共产党三十七周年生日\t李济深"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上下五千年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵横九万里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古今到中外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"功德孰比拟？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落后旧中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百几无一是。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孰知十年间？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面目全新矣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人民众，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人以散沙比。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日究如何？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结成一体。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族几十种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽见压迫史。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今究如何？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一大家庭似。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"封建几千年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民生活里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"救死犹不瞻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希暇顾廉耻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更是百年来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有帝国主义。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双斧伐枯树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一摘又再摘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国家与人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丧亡日在俟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芸芸苦大众，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喁喁怎望治？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朝救星来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻腾变天地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民得解放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自管自己事。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民作主人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风移俗也易。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都平等，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱如兄弟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民觉悟高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力量比原子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产力解放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民好生息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国家日富强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界刮目视。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进劲头大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人众真可恃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进劲鼓足，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一日廾年事。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"短期迈英伦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终能跨北美。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腐朽化神奇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消极变积极。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明明是人为，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相惊有神鬼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夫何使之然？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是党领导赐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的总领导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贤明毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天亶作聪明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔萃而出类。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自生民以来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未曾见有此。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党生卅七载，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正如方升日。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"普照人世间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万年无底止。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造福遍人寰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长寿齐天纪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛况激心情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝祷情难已。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}